---
// Hero Section - El Poder del Agradecimiento
---

<section class="hero-section bg-gradient-to-br from-purple to-blue min-h-screen flex items-center relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white opacity-5 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white opacity-5 rounded-full translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>

  <div class="container-custom section relative z-10">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Texto principal -->
      <div class="text-white text-center md:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          EL PODER DEL<br />
          <span class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">AGRADECIMIENTO</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 opacity-95">
          Cambia tu energía. Atrae abundancia. Vive en gratitud
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-10 opacity-90 max-w-xl">
          Descubre cómo el agradecimiento puede transformar tu vida, sanar tu cuerpo y
          atraer la abundancia que mereces. Un curso de 3 módulos para vivir en gratitud.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
          <a href="#precio" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-purple hover:bg-cream rounded-full font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl inline-block text-center">
            Acceder al Curso
          </a>
          <a href="#video" class="px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-purple rounded-full font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl inline-block text-center">
            Ver Video
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Imagen de Carolina -->
      <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-end">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white opacity-20 rounded-3xl transform rotate-6"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden max-w-md">
            <!-- Placeholder para la imagen de Carolina -->
            <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-light to-mauve flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center p-8">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-white opacity-30"></div>
                <p class="text-white text-lg font-semibold">Carolina Novoa</p>
                <p class="text-white text-sm opacity-80">Terapeuta Espiritual</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section {
      min-height: auto;
      padding-top: 4rem;
      padding-bottom: 4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
